  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The YP says that RETURNDATACOPY is zero padded, but [EIP 211](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-211) specifies it's an error to request data past the end of the buffer. [geth's implementation concurs](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/7504dbd6eb3f62371f86b06b03ffd665690951f2/core/vm/instructions.go#L470).",
